org.knime.core.node

Interface BufferedDataTable.KnowsRowCountTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataTable, Iterable<DataRow>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConcatenateTable, ContainerTable, ExtensionTable, JoinedTable, RearrangeColumnsTable, TableSpecReplacerTable, VoidTable, WrappedTable
    Enclosing class:
    BufferedDataTable

    public static interface BufferedDataTable.KnowsRowCountTable
extends DataTable
    Internally used interface. You won't have any benefit by implementing this interface! It's used for selected classes in the KNIME core.
    No public API: not to be implemented by clients
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.

      • checkRowCount

        static int checkRowCount(long count)
        Checks if the row count is greater than Integer.MAX_VALUE. If this is the case an exception is thrown, otherwise the number of rows is returned as an int.
        Parameters:
        count - the number of rows
        Returns:
        the number of rows
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if the number of rows is greater than Integer.MAX_VALUE
        Since:
        3.0
